imdb.plot outline: And so, Nerf Assassin has come back for a Season 2. Steph and Angela have been training for the Nerf battle of their lives for a prize of $5000 (that's enough to fund a web series). However, Joey tired from work wants to take a break. The girls have not broken the news to Joey and decide to tell him when they arrive to the location, but before they know it the battle royal starts. While the team seems to be holding off well, there's one assassin posing a threat to the dropouts' victory. The veteran assassin that put this whole game together beckons the team to give him the fight of his life. Flying foam and epic fake knife fights are sure to get you hyped.
imdb.title: Nerf Assassin: Season 2
